cs.CV, cs.CL, cs.MM, cs.IR, cs.LG. 

The paper deals with aligning videos with natural language descriptions, which involves both computer vision and natural language processing. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition). The paper also involves optimization and machine learning techniques, which could fall under categories such as cs.LG (Machine Learning) and cs.IR (Information Retrieval). Additionally, the use of natural language descriptions could also place the paper under cs.CL (Computation and Language) and cs.MM (Multimedia).
